{"name":"Paramnesia","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"trait","data":{"description":"<p>You have trouble distinguishing between real memories and fake ones &mdash;or ones that do not belong to you. Ths disorder has grown more common thanks to resleeving and the potential integration of memory artifacts in a morph&rsquo;s brain from a previous user to a later one. Some asyncs recall memories that are not transhuman.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 225","restrictions":"","triggers":"Alienation, immersion in water/vacuum, sex, the unknown","source":"ego","state":{"level":0,"triggered":false},"levels":[{"cost":2,"effects":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"You recall memories that are not real or not your own, or you may be confused about who, what, or where you are. Any superior failure on a skill test will result in you confusing important details.","id":"0zyge7dnuw"}],"id":"_defaultLevel"}],"subtype":"","traitType":"positive"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.Ri4FOaqxsl3hYaBh"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"OHymZBhed8NaXdHv"}
